ISLAMABAD, Aug 25 (APP): The employees of Election Commission of Pakistan (ECP) would donate one and two-day salary to support the flood victims, said spokesman of ECP.
In an effort to lend a helping hand amid this natural disaster, Chief Election Commissioner (CEC), Election Commissionâ€™s members and officers from Grade 17 to 22 would donate two-day salary, and the officials from BPS-7 to 16 would contribute one-day salary for the disaster relief fund, he said.
